                            <h2 id="3222"><a href="https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/">Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events</a></h2>
                            <p style="text-align: center"><span class='st_facebook' st_title='Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events' st_url='https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/'></span><span st_via='ohiotraveler' st_username='ohiotraveler' class='st_twitter' st_title='Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events' st_url='https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/'></span><span st_title='Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events' st_url='https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/' class='st_pinterest'></span><span st_title='Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events' st_url='https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/' class='st_linkedin'></span><span st_title='Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events' st_url='https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/' class='st_email'></span><span st_title='Ohio Christmas &#038; Holiday Events' st_url='https://www.ohiotraveler.com/ohio-christmas-holiday-fests-events/' class='st_sharethis'></span></p>
